001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 191,
009    displayName = "Version Info",
010    internalName = "LID_VERSION_INFO"
011)
012public class VersionInfoHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
013
014    private long version;
015    private long configABits;
016    private long configBBits;
017    private int armCrc;
018
019    public VersionInfoHistoryLog() {}
020    public VersionInfoHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long version, long configABits, long configBBits, int armCrc) {
021        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
022        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, version, configABits, configBBits, armCrc);
023        this.version = version;
024        this.configABits = configABits;
025        this.configBBits = configBBits;
026        this.armCrc = armCrc;
027
028    }
029
030    public VersionInfoHistoryLog(long version, long configABits, long configBBits, int armCrc) {
031        this(0, 0, version, configABits, configBBits, armCrc);
032    }
033
034    public int typeId() {
035        return 191;
036    }
037
038    /**
039     * <table border="1">
040     * <caption>Parsed fields for VersionInfoHistoryLog:</caption>
041     * <tr><td><code>version</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
042     * <tr><td><code>configABits</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
043     * <tr><td><code>configBBits</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
044     * <tr><td><code>armCrc</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 24)</code></td></tr>
045     * </table>
046     */
047    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
048        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
049        this.cargo = raw;
050        parseBase(raw);
051        this.version = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10);
052        this.configABits = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14);
053        this.configBBits = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
054        this.armCrc = Bytes.readShort(raw, 24);
055
056    }
057
058    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long version, long configABits, long configBBits, int armCrc) {
059        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
060            new byte[]{(byte) 191, 0},
061            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
062            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
063            Bytes.toUint32(version),
064            Bytes.toUint32(configABits),
065            Bytes.toUint32(configBBits),
066            new byte[]{0, 0},
067            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(armCrc)));
068    }
069
070    public long getVersion() {
071        return version;
072    }
073
074    public long getConfigABits() {
075        return configABits;
076    }
077
078    public long getConfigBBits() {
079        return configBBits;
080    }
081
082    public int getArmCrc() {
083        return armCrc;
084    }
085}
